Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> consulta
Rule 1     consulta -> busqueda
Rule 2     consulta -> stock
Rule 3     busqueda -> BUSCAR PRODUCTO IDENTIFICADOR
Rule 4     busqueda -> MOSTRAR PRODUCTOS condicion
Rule 5     stock -> VER STOCK IDENTIFICADOR
Rule 6     condicion -> filtro resto_condicion
Rule 7     resto_condicion -> Y filtro resto_condicion
Rule 8     resto_condicion -> empty
Rule 9     filtro -> SIN STOCK
Rule 10    filtro -> CON STOCK
Rule 11    filtro -> DE CATEGORIA IDENTIFICADOR
Rule 12    filtro -> CON PRECIO comparador NUMERO
Rule 13    comparador -> MAYOR_QUE
Rule 14    comparador -> MENOR_QUE
Rule 15    empty -> <empty>

